
========================================================
  GLIA — GNU/Linux + AI
========================================================

Your AI assistant is ready. Try:

  glia <request>         proposes a shell command (Enter = run)
  glia -d <question>     plain-text answer, no command
  glia -h                help (including how to rename it)

Dangerous commands always require typing YES.
Project: https://github.com/micheleperani76/GLIA

